"privacy_policy_content" = "Privacy Policy\n\nLast Updated: April 2026\n\n1. Data Collection\nDigital Compass reads device orientation sensors and location data (for Qibla direction calculation only).\n\n2. Data Usage\n- Location data is used solely for calculating Qibla direction\n- No account system or cloud sync\n- No personal information collected beyond functional requirements\n\n3. Data Storage\nAll data is stored locally on your device.\n\n4. Third Parties\nWe do not share data with third parties.\n\n5. Contact\nFor privacy questions, contact: support@digitalcompass.app";

"user_terms_content" = "Terms of Service\n\nLast Updated: April 2026\n\n1. Acceptance\nBy using Digital Compass, you agree to these terms.\n\n2. Use License\nDigital Compass is a tool reference application. Results depend on device state and environment.\n\n3. Disclaimer\n- Direction results are for reference only\n- Use in safe, legal environments\n- Do not rely solely for critical navigation\n\n4. Modifications\nWe reserve the right to update features, pricing, and terms.\n\n5. Limitation\nWe are not liable for damages from app use.";

"subscription_terms_content" = "Subscription Terms\n\nLast Updated: April 2026\n\n1. Auto-Renewal\nSubscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled 24 hours before period end.\n\n2. Payment\nCharged to Apple account.\n\n3. Cancellation\nCancel anytime in Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions.\n\n4. Refunds\nHandled per Apple's policy.\n\n5. Restore\nRestore purchases on any device with the same Apple ID.";

