"help_page_content" = "How to use\n\n• Open the app: direction text and 0–359° update in real time when the device has a digital compass.\n\n• Precision: the bar and label show Good / Fair / Poor. Use Calibrate to follow the 8-figure pattern when readings are unstable.\n\n• Qibla: allow location (while in use) to compute the bearing to Mecca. Reposition if you have moved a long distance.\n\n• Pro: removes ads, unlocks advanced themes and dial styles, and future premium options via subscription. Restore purchases in Settings with the same Apple ID.\n\nNote: This app is a reference tool; do not use as the only source for safety-critical navigation.";
